### CopyAI API

To use the AI generation feature, you need a Hugging Face token.

1. Get a token from https://huggingface.co/settings/tokens
2. Create a `.env.local` file in the `app/` directory with:

```
HF_TOKEN=your_hugging_face_token_here
```

The API route will use this token to call the Hugging Face Inference API.
